commit.message:
allow absolute GNU install dirs (#1092)

CMAKE_INSTALL_*DIR are allowed to be absolute, so they shouldn't be
appended to other paths. Instead, use CMAKE_INSTALL_FULL_*DIR, which are
known to be absolute.
